  <thing id="raAP66SihV" name="Sihedron Vulnerability" description="A creature equipped with the Sihedron can penetrate the clockwork reliquary&apos;s damage reduction with any attack, and automatically succeeds\nat all checks to penetrate its spell resistance. If the Sihedron&apos;s user transfers the Sihedron to an ally while the clockwork reliquary is within 30 feet, the reliquary must succeed at a DC 30 Fortitude save or be staggered for 1 round." compset="RaceSpec">
